    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0750a13"/><head><date from-iso="0947-03-15" key="j20670182068464" to-iso="0951-02-28">漢</date><placeName key="PL000000023564">洛陽天宮寺</placeName><persName key="A009958">從隱</persName>傳（<persName key="A009963">夢江</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0750a14"/><persName key="A009958">釋從隱</persName>，姓劉氏，<placeName key="PL000000023795">洛陽三鄉</placeName>人也。丱年敏慧，誓<lb
ed="T" n="0750a15"/>欲出塵，二親既聽，乃投本邑<placeName key="PL000000023767">竹閣院</placeName>，依師<lb
ed="T" n="0750a16"/>誦習，陶練靈府。尋於<placeName key="PL000000023260">嵩陽</placeName>受戒畢，就<placeName key="PL000000023817">長水</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0750a17"/>聽采，纔歷數年，克通《百法》、《中觀》、《彌陀》三經論<lb
ed="T" n="0750a18"/>焉。而<persName key="A009885">諲師</persName>年老，深許<persName key="A009958">隱</persName>之博達性相。後於<lb
ed="T" n="0750a19"/>洛<placeName key="PL000000023571">布金院</placeName>赴請敷演。至<date from-iso="0934" key="j20623522063248" to-iso="0936">後唐清泰</date>中，<persName key="A009885">諲</persName>付<lb
ed="T" n="0750a20"/>講座，日為眾三登法席。夏中長晷，覽《藏經》<lb
ed="T" n="0750a21"/>一袟，精進苦節，人無與比。<date from-iso="0949-02-06" key="j20677122067741" to-iso="0949-03-07">乾祐二年正月</date>，示<lb
ed="T" n="0750a22"/>疾而終，俗壽五十三，僧臘三十二。乃依天<lb
ed="T" n="0750a23"/>竺法火化，收合真體，圓淨堪愛，門人樹塔，<lb
ed="T" n="0750a24"/>至今存焉。次有<placeName key="PL000000023804">長水縣<anchor xml:id="beg0750002"/>縣<anchor xml:id="end0750002"/>泉院</placeName><persName key="A009963">釋夢江</persName>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0750a25"/>姓楊氏，<placeName key="PL000000023817">本邑</placeName>人也。神彩灑落，超拔凡態，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0750a26"/>願出家，恒誦《仁王》、《般若》。進具後講《百法論》。<lb
ed="T" n="0750a27"/><date from-iso="0934" key="j20623522063248" to-iso="0936">清泰</date>中<placeName key="PL000000023667">龍門廣化寺</placeName>請為眾開演，遇<ref type="person" target="#A006578">帝</ref>幸其<lb
ed="T" n="0750a28"/><placeName key="PL000000023667">寺</placeName>宣問，妙辯天逸，悅可上心，時於御前賜<lb
ed="T" n="0750a29"/>紫袈裟，確乎不受。訓導二十餘年，講罷行道<pb ed="T" n="0750b" xml:id="T50.2061.0750b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0750b01"/><anchor xml:id="beg0750sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0750sgsz1"/>佛，日唯一食。慈忍於物，罕逢慍色。<date from-iso="0956-02-20" key="j20702822070635" to-iso="0957-02-07">周顯<lb
ed="T" n="0750b02"/>德三年</date>疾終，緇素悲慕，為其建塔矣。</p>
